Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image contain a pair of spaniels?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image contain a pair of spaniels?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a black-and-white dog in the pair of spaniels?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a black-and-white dog in the pair of spaniels?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} and {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
